{"tid":2105763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[提早放暑假] 有幾多學校嘅學生係繼續翻緊學？","createTime":"2020-07-13T00:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:11:44.000Z","uid":350891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8651117a9ba2bf630cecde910b93026272fa18b","tid":2105763,"uid":350891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:53:59.000Z","msg":"[蘋果] 本港自周日（5日）再出現本地感染個案後，連日來有增無減，更有多間學校因有學生、學生親屬或教職員的家人染疫而需要停課。教育局局長楊潤雄今午表示，由於過去兩日武漢肺炎個案急升，政府已宣佈明起收緊社交距離措施，教育局經過考慮後，全港中小學及幼稚園可於下星期一起開始提早放暑假。<br />\n<br />\n葉建源：疫情若持續惡化 局方應給予更明確的指示<br />\n<br />\n葉又表示，認同局方容許中學自行決定高中考試及暑期補課的安排，但疫情若持續惡化，局方應給予更明確的指示，「假如（疫情）惡化落去，係唔係仲係由學校自己決定補唔補課呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n教育局只係宣布提早放暑假，其實有好多野都係推俾學校去決定，學生可以繼續考試, 對卷, 補課，所以要中招嘅仍然可以中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46704775447217524b8fd2240526ec117585323","tid":2105763,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1ad5087ffff0459fafabab66dad987a96d5271e","tid":2105763,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"今朝搭車返工仲見到好多中小學生著住校服返學"},{"pid":"2763ae2793a3e273b51e51b0a4944dc99de79d78","tid":2105763,"uid":350891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1ad5087ffff0459fafabab66dad987a96d5271e","tid":2105763,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"今朝搭車返工仲見到好多中小學生著住校服返學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"有好多學校仍然要翻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde1048cdf7f949ca042da463e00f607b90fbe35","tid":2105763,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"好多學校講就話放暑假 但係就用暑期班做借口叫學生反"},{"pid":"a1c798324c2a7bc8fb9e43c4a8799660dd403bd8","tid":2105763,"uid":45293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"樓下間中學仲見學生返學"},{"pid":"ca6139e24d9df980a20e96141b79a713ef929676","tid":2105763,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:09:49.000Z","msg":"on9暑假唔補課點趕進度<br />\n你估停咗課咁耐唔使還呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359219bf1c70581a394c0299fe5f4815c12ca36b","tid":2105763,"uid":350891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c798324c2a7bc8fb9e43c4a8799660dd403bd8","tid":2105763,"uid":45293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"樓下間中學仲見學生返學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"應該仲有一半嘅學生都要翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}